# Plug & Play repo context

- **Stack**: Vite + React + TypeScript, D3, Jotai, Tailwind + shadcn/ui.
- **Entry docs**: read `AGENTS.md`, then `README.md`, then `src/README.md`.
- **Key areas**:
  - `src/core/`: infrastructure (RPC, storage, data-engine)
  - `src/state/`: Jotai atoms (UI + data)
  - `src/d3-core/`: chart engine + renderer/scales/axes
  - `src/compute/` + `src/engine/`: heavy compute + workers

## Development expectations

- Prefer `@/` imports.
- Keep heavy work out of React render paths.
- Don’t introduce broad re-render cascades (especially charts and large lists).

